            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## MacHelper Pro 1.0.0 (12)

- Fixes Finder right-click menu actions in installed builds by resolving Finder-rewritten menu identifiers.
- Uses a sandbox-safe app handoff so Terminal, editor, VSCode, Codex, and custom app actions run reliably.
- Adds regression coverage for Finder context menu action identity resolution.
]]></description>
