            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## MacHelper Pro 1.0.0 (11)

- Fixes Finder right-click menu clicks so action identifiers survive Finder menu dispatch and the selected action can run.
- Routes Finder open actions through the same command path for configured editors, terminals, Codex, VSCode, and custom apps.
- Keeps Finder action success diagnostics at debug level to avoid noisy public logs.
]]></description>
